SubjectCarrry The Kettle Nakoda First Nation N° 76-59, Saskatchewan ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of the power to take an interest in lands within CARRY THE KETTLE NAKODA FIRST NATION N° 76-59, Saskatchewan; and (b) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the grant of the required easement.
